Package: modArtist
Title: Artist Profile Module for Artalytics Platform
Version: 0.0.7
Authors@R:
    person("Bobby", "Fatemi", , "bobby@artalytics.app", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Shiny module for displaying artist profile pages with featured artwork,
    bio, collections overview, and recent works. Supports shareable URLs via artist
    slugs and respects collection visibility settings from the artist settings system.
License: file LICENSE
